@Deprecated
public class MetaioCloudARViewActivity
extends MetaioCloudViewActivity
implements MetaioSurfaceView.Callback

This is metaio Cloud AR view activity. It may be executed with default behavior, however for customized behavior and GUI, this should be extended and relevant methods should be overridden.
